### **3ï¸âƒ£ DAO (`UserDAO.java`)**
```java
public class UserDAO {
    public List<User> searchByKeyword(String keyword) {
        try (SqlSession session = MyBatisUtil.getSession()) {
            return session.selectList("UserMapper.searchByKeyword", keyword);
        }
    }
}
```
